        },
        {
          "md": "GPS 175, GNC 355/355A, and GNX 375 are the first 2” by 6.25” panel mount navigators to employ full color capacitive touchscreen technology.",
          "value": "GPS 175, GNC 355/355A, and GNX 375 are the first 2” by 6.25” panel mount navigators to employ full color capacitive touchscreen technology.",
